
=========
ProtoWiki
=========

Use gf to open a ProtoWiki page.

Add this to your .vimrc file::

    :map gf :e <cfile><CR>
    :command UpdateIndex r!ls | grep -v html 


To update the Index do this::

    :UpdateIndex

To build restructured text HTML files from your wiki files:

    :!fab build

To clean up the html:

    :!fab clean

To commit/push the changes:

    :!fab save:comment="New changes!"


To pull new changes:
    
    :!fab pull

